2. [출제의도] 상황에 적절한 응답을 고른다.
M: You have a Band­Aid on your hand. What 
happened?
W: My cat scratched me when I tried to clip his 
nails.
M: Did you see a doctor? It might get infected.
W:                                               
scratch 할퀴다
